    <item>
      <title>machine learning: the big picture (before you learn anything else)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/third_post/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/third_post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;this is post zero of my ml journey. before i dive into any single algorithm, i wanted to build the full map first — so every future topic has somewhere to land.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;here&amp;rsquo;s everything i wish someone had shown me on day one.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xD;&#xA;@import url(&#39;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&amp;family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&amp;family=Barlow:wght@400;500;600;700;900&amp;display=swap&#39;);&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-breakout {&#xD;&#xA;  width: 100vw;&#xD;&#xA;  position: relative;&#xD;&#xA;  left: 50%;&#xD;&#xA;  right: 50%;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-left: -50vw;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-right: -50vw;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 24px;&#xD;&#xA;  box-sizing: border-box;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-wrap {&#xD;&#xA;  max-width: 1100px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 auto;&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Barlow&#39;, sans-serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 16px;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 48px 0 64px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-hero {&#xD;&#xA;  background: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 40px 48px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xD;&#xA;  align-items: center;&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 0;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 4px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-hero-quote {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 1.25rem;&#xD;&#xA;  font-style: italic;&#xD;&#xA;  flex: 1;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.65;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 40px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-stat {&#xD;&#xA;  text-align: center;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 36px;&#xD;&#xA;  border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);&#xD;&#xA;  flex-shrink: 0;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-stat-num {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 2.8rem;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 900;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-stat-lbl {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.18em;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  opacity: 0.45;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-top: 6px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-rule {&#xD;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xD;&#xA;  align-items: center;&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 18px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 52px 0 28px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-rule-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #1a1408; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-rule-text {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 11px;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.22em;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 600;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #7a6f5a;&#xD;&#xA;  white-space: nowrap;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-grid {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 16px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-item {&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 22px 24px;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  border-left: 4px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.6;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-item.hl { border-left-color: #c0392b; background: rgba(192,57,43,0.04); }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-item strong {&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 15px;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 6px;&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Barlow&#39;, sans-serif;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-item .mlov-formula {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 14px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 6px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-vs-item .mlov-desc { color: #7a6f5a; font-size: 14px; }&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-needs {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 16px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-need {&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 22px 24px;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  border-left: 4px solid #1a3a5c;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-need strong {&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 16px;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 6px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-need span { color: #7a6f5a; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; display: block; }&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-grid {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 1px;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-card {&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 32px 26px;&#xD;&#xA;  cursor: pointer;&#xD;&#xA;  transition: background 0.18s;&#xD;&#xA;  position: relative;&#xD;&#xA;  overflow: hidden;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-card:hover { background: #ffeaa0; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-card.mlov-active { background: #1a1408; color: #f5f0e8; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pnum {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 4rem;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 900;&#xD;&#xA;  opacity: 0.07;&#xD;&#xA;  position: absolute;&#xD;&#xA;  top: 4px; right: 12px;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-picon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-card h3 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 1.25rem !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 10px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.3;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-card p {&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 14px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  opacity: 0.7;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.6;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-hint {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.15em;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  opacity: 0.4;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-top: 16px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-detail {&#xD;&#xA;  background: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 36px 40px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: none;&#xD;&#xA;  animation: mlov-fadein 0.25s ease;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;@keyframes mlov-fadein { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-detail.mlov-active {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 32px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-detail h4 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 10px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.22em;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  opacity: 0.4;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 10px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-paradigm-detail p { font-size: 14px !important; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 12px !important; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 8px; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-chip {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 11px;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 4px 12px;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);&#xD;&#xA;  color: #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.04em;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 28px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-col h3 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 1.25rem !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 14px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding-bottom: 12px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border-bottom: 2px solid currentColor !important;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.3;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-col.classical h3 { color: #1a3a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-col.deep h3 { color: #c0392b; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-col.modern h3 { color: #3d1a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-topic {&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 11px 14px;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 5px;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 14px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xD;&#xA;  align-items: center;&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  transition: transform 0.12s, box-shadow 0.12s;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-topic:hover { transform: translateX(5px); }&#xD;&#xA;.classical .mlov-map-topic:hover { box-shadow: -4px 0 0 #1a3a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.deep .mlov-map-topic:hover { box-shadow: -4px 0 0 #c0392b; }&#xD;&#xA;.modern .mlov-map-topic:hover { box-shadow: -4px 0 0 #3d1a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }&#xD;&#xA;.classical .mlov-dot { background: #1a3a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.deep .mlov-dot { background: #c0392b; }&#xD;&#xA;.modern .mlov-dot { background: #3d1a5c; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-name { flex: 1; font-weight: 500; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-map-note {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 11px;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #7a6f5a;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipeline {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  overflow: hidden;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe {&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 28px 20px;&#xD;&#xA;  border-right: 1px solid #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;  transition: background 0.15s;&#xD;&#xA;  position: relative;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe:last-child { border-right: none; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe:hover { background: #ffeaa0; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe-num {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 3.2rem;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 900;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 8px;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe h4 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 13px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.07em;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 8px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe p { font-size: 13px !important; color: #7a6f5a; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 !important; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-pipe-arrow {&#xD;&#xA;  position: absolute;&#xD;&#xA;  right: -10px; top: 50%;&#xD;&#xA;  transform: translateY(-50%);&#xD;&#xA;  background: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  width: 20px; height: 20px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  z-index: 2;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concepts {&#xD;&#xA;  display: grid;&#xD;&#xA;  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);&#xD;&#xA;  gap: 1px;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concept {&#xD;&#xA;  background: #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 26px 24px;&#xD;&#xA;  transition: background 0.15s;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concept:hover { background: #fff8ee; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concept .ctag {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.18em;&#xD;&#xA;  text-transform: uppercase;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #7a6f5a;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 8px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concept h4 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 1.05rem !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 8px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.3;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-concept p { font-size: 14px !important; color: #5a5045; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 !important; }&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-timeline-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0 56px; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-timeline::before {&#xD;&#xA;  content: &#39;&#39;; position: absolute;&#xD;&#xA;  left: 8px; top: 8px; bottom: 0;&#xD;&#xA;  width: 1px; background: #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-tl { position: relative; padding-bottom: 28px; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-tl::before {&#xD;&#xA;  content: &#39;&#39;; position: absolute;&#xD;&#xA;  left: -27px; top: 7px;&#xD;&#xA;  width: 10px; height: 10px;&#xD;&#xA;  border-radius: 50%;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;  border: 2px solid #f5f0e8;&#xD;&#xA;  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #1a1408;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-tl-year {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;IBM Plex Mono&#39;, monospace;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 11px;&#xD;&#xA;  color: #c0392b;&#xD;&#xA;  letter-spacing: 0.12em;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 600;&#xD;&#xA;  margin-bottom: 4px;&#xD;&#xA;  display: block;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-tl h4 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 15px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 4px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-tl p { font-size: 14px !important; color: #7a6f5a; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 !important; }&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;.mlov-mental { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 18px; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-mental-card {&#xD;&#xA;  border: 1px solid #c8bfaa;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 28px 26px;&#xD;&#xA;  background: #fff8ee;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-mental-card .mletter { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-mental-card h4 {&#xD;&#xA;  font-family: &#39;Playfair Display&#39;, Georgia, serif;&#xD;&#xA;  font-size: 1.1rem !important;&#xD;&#xA;  font-weight: 700;&#xD;&#xA;  margin: 0 0 8px !important;&#xD;&#xA;  padding: 0 !important;&#xD;&#xA;  border: none !important;&#xD;&#xA;  line-height: 1.3;&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;.mlov-mental-card p { font-size: 14px !important; color: #5a5045; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 !important; }&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; &#xD;&#xA;@media (max-width: 900px) {&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 20px; padding: 28px 24px; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-stat { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); padding: 16px 0 0; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-hero-quote { padding: 0; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-paradigm-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-paradigm-detail.mlov-active { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-map, .mlov-timeline-grid, .mlov-mental { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-pipeline { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-pipe { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1408; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-pipe-arrow { display: none; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-concepts { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-vs-grid, .mlov-needs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-wrap { padding: 24px 0 40px; }&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;@media (max-width: 600px) {&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-paradigm-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;  .mlov-concepts { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }&#xD;&#xA;}&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;mlov-breakout&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;mlov-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-hero&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-stat&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-num&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-lbl&#34;&gt;Core Paradigms&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-hero-quote&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &#34;Teaching machines to learn from experience, rather than programming every rule by hand — that is the essence of the entire field.&#34;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-stat&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-num&#34;&gt;~70yr&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-lbl&#34;&gt;History of ML&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-stat&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-num&#34;&gt;∞&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-stat-lbl&#34;&gt;Applications&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-text&#34;&gt;§ 1 — Traditional Programming vs Machine Learning&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-vs-grid&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-vs-item&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;Traditional Programming&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-formula&#34;&gt;Data + Rules → Output&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-desc&#34;&gt;You write the if/else. The computer executes exactly what you tell it.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-vs-item hl&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;Machine Learning&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-formula&#34;&gt;Data + Output → Rules&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-desc&#34;&gt;You show examples. The computer finds the rules itself.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-vs-item&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;Deep Learning&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-formula&#34;&gt;Raw Data + Output → Complex Rules&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-desc&#34;&gt;Learns layered representations automatically, end-to-end.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-text&#34;&gt;The Three Things Every ML System Needs&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-needs&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-need&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;📊 Data&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span&gt;Examples of inputs and (usually) outputs. The raw material. Garbage in, garbage out.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-need&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;🧮 A Model&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span&gt;A mathematical function that maps inputs to outputs. Its internal parameters are what get learned.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-need&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;strong&gt;📉 A Loss Function&lt;/strong&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span&gt;A way to measure how wrong the model is right now — so it knows which direction to improve.&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-text&#34;&gt;§ 2 — The Four Learning Paradigms · click to expand&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-rule-line&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-paradigm-grid&#34; id=&#34;mlov-pgrid&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-paradigm-card&#34; data-idx=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;mlov-pnum&#34;&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;span class=&#34;mlov-picon&#34;&gt;🎓&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;h3&gt;Supervised Learning&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;      &lt;p&gt;Learn from labelled examples. You tell the machine the right answer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>how google docs lets 100 people type at once (without everything exploding)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/second_post/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/second_post/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;somewhere in google&amp;rsquo;s infrastructure, right now, thousands of people are typing into the same documents simultaneously. cursors flying, edits overlapping, nobody waiting for anyone else. and somehow — through what looks like pure coordination magic, everyone ends up with the same document.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;it&amp;rsquo;s one of those things that feels obvious until you try to explain how it works. then it gets interesting fast.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;i started pulling on this thread after a perfectly ordinary tuesday afternoon where a friend and i typed over each other in a shared doc and nothing broke. that shouldn&amp;rsquo;t be as hard as it is. here&amp;rsquo;s why it is, and how google solved it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>understanding shells &amp; commands: because i was lost too (part1)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/first_post1/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/first_post1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.notion.so/Understanding-Shells-Commands-Because-I-Was-Lost-Too-2f42da7f7c25805383b2e2068ea1ca0b&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; class=&#34;notion-btn&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;  read on notion ↗&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;look, i&amp;rsquo;ll be honest — i spent way too long just copying and running commands without actually understanding what was happening. everyone around me seemed to know what they were doing in the terminal, and i just&amp;hellip; didn&amp;rsquo;t. i&amp;rsquo;d paste commands, pray they worked, and move on.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;the problem? nobody actually explains what a shell &lt;em&gt;is&lt;/em&gt; before throwing you into it. we all start learning python or java or whatever, and suddenly professors are like &amp;ldquo;yeah just cd into this directory and run this&amp;rdquo; and you&amp;rsquo;re sitting there like&amp;hellip; what&amp;rsquo;s cd? what&amp;rsquo;s a directory? why does this black window exist?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
